    "Therefore, we acknowledge some of the challenges in strictly defining disinformation, as reflected in its different definitions in the EU regulatory landscape.",
    "However, for the purposes of this paper, we highlight that the various definitions of disinformation allow it to be characterized as an umbrella term.",
